        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nI believe there is an issue with the build. After the first build (maven clean install), the Grizzly server gave me a not found for the root context, after running the org.onap.policy.gui.editors.apex.rest.ApexEditorMain class. On the second build though, it worked.\nI've tried also in a clean repo folder, and got the same behavior.\nNot sure what is happening.",
